OL,7,FThe Women Against State Pension
OL,8,FInequality (Waspi) campaign has sent a
OL,9,F"letter before action" to the
OL,10,FDepartment for Work and Pensions
OL,11,F(DWP), warning of High Court
OL,12,Fproceedings if the issue is not
OL,13,Fresolved.
OL,15,FAngela Madden, chairwoman of the
OL,16,Fgroup, said members will not allow the
OL,17,FDWP's "gaslighting" of Waspi women to
OL,18,Fgo "unchallenged".
