OL,7,FWaspi campaigners says the
OL,8,FGovernment's reasons for rejecting the
OL,9,FParliamentary and Health Service
OL,10,FOmbudsman (PHSO) report, which found
OL,11,Fthat the women should be paid up to
OL,12,F#2,950 each, are "legally wrong".
OL,14,FThe group, which has launched a
OL,15,F#75,000 Crowdjustice campaign to fund
OL,16,Flegal action, says the Government has
OL,17,F14 days to respond before the case is
OL,18,Ffiled.
