OL,7,FThe Prime Minister, Chancellor Rachel
OL,8,FReeves and Work and Pensions Secretary
OL,9,FLiz Kendall, who ruled out a
OL,10,Fcompensation package, are among the
OL,11,Fsenior ministers who backed the Waspi
OL,12,Fcampaign when Labour was in opposition.
OL,14,FAbout 3.6 million women in the UK were
OL,15,Faffected by the change, first
OL,16,Fannounced in the 1990s, to bring their
OL,17,Fretirement age in line with men.
