OL,7,FThis was later accelerated under the
OL,8,FConservative-Liberal Democrat
OL,9,Fcoalition government more than a
OL,10,Fdecade ago.
OL,12,FHowever, there was a 28-month delay in
OL,13,Fwriting to inform them of the changes,
OL,14,Fwhich the Government accepted and
OL,15,Fapologised for.
OL,17,FThe Government previously highlighted
OL,18,Fresearch indicating that, by 2006, 90%
OL,19,Fof 1950s-born women knew about state
OL,20,Fpension age changes.
