OL,7,FWaspi campaigners have claimed women
OL,8,Fsuffered financial hardship and had to
OL,9,Frethink retirement plans.
OL,11,FMs Madden said: "The Government has
OL,12,Faccepted that 1950s-born women are
OL,13,Fvictims of maladministration, but it
OL,14,Fnow says none of us suffered any
OL,15,Finjustice.
OL,17,F"We believe this is not only an
OL,18,Foutrage but legally wrong."
