OL,7,FShe added: "We have been successful
OL,8,Fbefore and we are confident we will be
OL,9,Fagain.
OL,11,F"But what would be better for everyone
OL,12,Fis if the Secretary of State now saw
OL,13,Fsense and came to the table to sort
OL,14,Fout a compensation package.
OL,16,F"The alternative is continued defence
OL,17,Fof the indefensible but this time in
OL,18,Ffront of a judge."
