OL,7,FA Government spokesperson said: "We
OL,8,Faccept the Ombudsman's finding of
OL,9,Fmaladministration and have apologised
OL,10,Ffor there being a 28-month delay in
OL,11,Fwriting to 1950s-born women.
OL,13,F"However, evidence showed only one in
OL,14,Ffour people remember reading and
OL,15,Freceiving letters that they weren't
OL,16,Fexpecting and that by 2006 90% of
OL,17,F1950s-born women knew that the state
OL,18,Fpension age was changing.
OL,20,F"Earlier letters wouldn't have
OL,21,Faffected this.
